name: The Flip
summary:
A super fun zombie shooter** 🧟 - GingasVR

👾 **The Flip is the perfect game!** 🌟 - turbotek_td

👀 **The biggest hordes yet to be seen on the Quest headset** 🕶️ - Mac in VR

🤝 **A great multiplayer experience** 🎉 - FluffySez


**The Flip** is the cooperative VR shooter you’ve been waiting for! Flip City is overrun with the undead and it’s up to intrepid survivors to blast through the hordes. Filled with ravenous nano-tech-infused zombie hordes, jump into missions solo or better yet, team up with...
